    </div>
    <main>
      <div class="pt-40 pb-32">
        <div id="features" class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wider" style="color: #a855f7;">核心优势</h3>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl mt-2 max-w-3xl" style="color: #1a1a2e;">为什么选择 weelinking？</h2>
          <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:mt-16 lg:grid-cols-6 lg:grid-rows-3">
            <div class="fade-in-up card-enhanced relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl p-8 lg:col-span-2" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); backdrop-filter: blur(20px); border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wider" style="color: #a855f7;">模型覆盖</div>
              <h3 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight " style="color: #1a1a2e;">200+ AI 大模型全覆盖</h3>
